components.waypointcard

Class WaypointCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.layout.Region
          • javafx.scene.layout.Pane
            • javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane
              • components.waypointcard.WaypointCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IWaypointCard<AbstractWaypoint>, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class WaypointCard
extends javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane
implements IWaypointCard<AbstractWaypoint>
    This component is a wrapper for a DeliveryAddressCard or WarehouseCard. It chooses the best concrete card according to the type of the `waypoint` property.
